physical_examinations.relevant_findings: General: Alert and oriented, no acute distress. HEENT: No scleral icterus, mucous membranes moist. Cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs/gallops/rubs. Pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes/rhonchi/rales. Abdomen: Soft, nondistended, nontender, no rebound or guarding, normoactive bowel sounds, no palpable masses. Digital Rectal Exam: Normal tone, no gross or occult blood. Extremities: No edema, warm and well perfused.
